des: The Bell Cultural Events Center is available for use by the surrounding community as well as the MNU campus community. This facility is used to showcase the talents of the MNU Fine and Performing Arts students and local artist and performing arts companies. You can rent many of the rooms within this state-of-the-art facility for events or performances.
